Black should hit the vital point at 1. Even though White can capture this stone with 2, Black will raise the sacrifice at 3 and then cut at 5 to squeeze the white stones. This capturing technique is called "stone pagoda' and makes sure to allow White no more than two liberties to win the capturing race.

